parameters.name: Net Body Balance
parameters.description: Fluid balance: net value over 24 hours, reset at midnight

parameters.name: VT/kg
parameters.description: Tidal volume per kg of ideal body weight

parameters.name: Position
parameters.description: Is the patient prone or supine

parameters.name: Hours in position
parameters.description: Number of hours in current position. (Note: if more than 3 days invalid and do not display).

parameters.name: P/F ratio
parameters.description: PaO2/FiO2, indicates severity of lung disease

parameters.name: Dynamic compliance
parameters.description: Ventilator parameter ~ tidal volume/(inspiratory pressure - PEEP)

parameters.name: Physiological deadspace
parameters.description: Ventilator parameter ~ tidal volume * ventilator ratio

parameters.name: Treadtable deadspace
parameters.description: Ventilator parameter ~ physiological deadspace - (Ideal body weight * 2.2)

parameters.name: RSBI
parameters.description: Rapid shallow breathing index ~ spontaneous RR / tidal volume in litres

parameters.name: Duration of mechanical ventilation
parameters.description: How many hours has this patient been on a ventilator

parameters.name: Sedated
parameters.description: String indicating names and dosages of sedatives (if in use).

parameters.name: Nutrition
parameters.description: String indication type of feeding in use (enternal, parenteral, jejunal)

parameters.name: Haemofiltration
parameters.description: Boolean indicating presence of renal support.
